<sect1 id="WHICH">
  <!-- DNT-Start --><title>WHICH</title><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para><emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->WHICH<!-- DNT-End --><indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->WHICH<!-- DNT-End --></primary>
    </indexterm><indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->WHICH<!-- DNT-End --> Function</primary>
    </indexterm>(</emphasis><emphasis>condition,â¦,condition</emphasis><emphasis
  role="bold">)</emphasis></para>

  <para><informaltable colsep="1" frame="all" rowsep="1">
      <tgroup cols="2">
        <colspec colwidth="78.20pt" />

        <colspec colwidth="274.60pt" />

        <tbody>
          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start --><emphasis>condition</emphasis><!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry>A conditional expression to evaluate.</entry>
          </row>

          <row>
            <entry><!-- DNT-Start -->Return:<!-- DNT-End --></entry>

            <entry><!-- DNT-Start -->WHICH<!-- DNT-End --> returns a single value.</entry>
          </row>
        </tbody>
      </tgroup>
    </informaltable></para>

  <para>The <emphasis role="bold"><!-- DNT-Start -->WHICH<!-- DNT-End --> </emphasis>function evaluates which of
  the list of <emphasis>conditions</emphasis> returned true and returns its
  ordinal position in the list of <emphasis>conditions</emphasis>. Returns
  zero (0) if none return true. This is the opposite of the <!-- DNT-Start -->REJECTED<!-- DNT-End -->
  function<indexterm>
      <primary><!-- DNT-Start -->REJECTED<!-- DNT-End --> function</primary>
    </indexterm>.</para>

  <para>Example:</para>

  <!-- DNT-Start --><programlisting>  Accept := WHICH(Person.per_first_name = 'Fred',
  Person.per_first_name = 'Sue');
  //Accept is 0 for everyone but those named Fred or Sue
</programlisting><!-- DNT-End -->

  <para>See Also: <link linkend="REJECTED"><!-- DNT-Start -->REJECTED<!-- DNT-End --></link>, <link linkend="MAP"><!-- DNT-Start -->MAP<!-- DNT-End --></link>, <link linkend="CHOOSE"><!-- DNT-Start -->CHOOSE<!-- DNT-End --></link>, <link linkend="IF"><!-- DNT-Start -->IF<!-- DNT-End --></link>, <link linkend="CASE"><!-- DNT-Start -->CASE<!-- DNT-End --></link></para>
</sect1>
